{"tid":2281325,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"旺角騷亂游泳教練縱火罪成候判 練錦鴻斥「呢單嘢都幾耐之前」促控方解釋","createTime":"2020-11-11T06:13:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-11T07:45:54.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6f4da1358cd318fecb213713de766b6efacd3dbf","tid":2281325,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T06:13:05.000Z","msg":"2016年旺角騷亂距今已逾四年半，仍有案件未完成審理。一名游泳教練被指當日扯下橫額丟進火堆，被控縱火罪受審。被告辯稱當時出於一片好心善意，鞏固路障以免加劇警民衝突，未有留意雜物堆中已有火舌。不過，法官練錦鴻認為被告的說法猶如出自一個夢遊的人或智力有問題的人，有歪常理，不接納被告說法，裁定被告縱火罪成，還柙至明早以待辯方大狀求情。<br />\n<br />\n法官練錦鴻今裁決指，當時情況危險，被告站在人群前，若發生衝突必定首當其衝。練官更形容被告的說法，猶如出自一個夢遊的人或智力有問題的人，有歪常理。而被告的描述亦與影片內容不符，因其他人可從路障旁的空隙穿過。練官裁定被告縱火罪成，並將他還柙至明天，待辯方準備求情陳詞。<br />\n<br />\n練官直言「呢單嘢都幾耐之前」，明白當中或因疫情致令聆訊延誤，亦知悉代表另兩名被告的大狀直指控方延誤檢控，著控方下次須就此解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201111/WYQFYIMPYNHFTE2TVEJS3JU3GY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201111%2FWYQFYIMPYNHFTE2TVEJS3JU3GY%2F&d=yH4nd0T6GS6ufvAy6eHVEb4BfDbUEiSkD5bB26vbFoA%3D&h=da031d62\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201111%2FWYQFYIMPYNHFTE2TVEJS3JU3GY%2F&h=51ab10cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201111/WYQFYIMPYNHFTE2TVEJS3JU3GY/</a>"},{"pid":"52ddd9c113833196c5f09fa08fcf479d9bf309d1","tid":2281325,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T06:15:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c8f3138f4c8b42088d2c3205582571f940727b4","tid":2281325,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T07:42:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0432ca2bf98e993d8c78935ecdfcde0531532b9","tid":2281325,"uid":40763,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T07:45:54.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<br />\n好撚煩 香港成班撚樣"}]}